.SH NAME
vmw_kms_check_display_memory \- Validates display memory required for a topology
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" vmw_kms_check_display_memory
.BI "(struct drm_device *dev "  ","
.BI "uint32_t num_rects "  ","
.BI "struct drm_rect *rects "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
DRM device
.IP "num_rects" 12
number of drm_rect in rects
.IP "rects" 12
array of drm_rect representing the topology to validate indexed by
crtc index.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success otherwise negative error code
